<script>
    grecaptcha.ready(function () {
        if (document.getElementById('captcha') != undefined) { 
            grecaptcha.execute('6Lcd2KoUAAAAAKtp6iVTJy1GQ3ZmgZTib7eD-B_O', { action: 'pageLoad' }).then(function (token) {
                $.ajax({
                    contentType: 'application/json; charset=utf-8',
                    dataType: 'json',
                    type: 'POST',
                    url: '/login/validatecaptcha?token=' + token,
                    success: function (response) {
                        if (response == false) { 
                            grecaptcha.render('captcha', {
                                'sitekey': '6Le5MasUAAAAABMJhGpyHQfNtnAlWP9wdhzc3GxD',
                                'callback': captchaCallback
                            });
                            document.getElementById('RequireCaptcha').value = 'true';
                            setV3CaptchaToken(false);
                        }
                        else {
                            setV3CaptchaToken(true);
                        }
                    }
                });
            });
        }
    });

    function setV3CaptchaToken(enableLogin) {
        if (document.getElementById('CaptchaToken') != undefined) {
            grecaptcha.execute('6Lcd2KoUAAAAAKtp6iVTJy1GQ3ZmgZTib7eD-B_O', { action: 'pageLoad' }).then(function (token) {
                document.getElementById('CaptchaToken').value = token;
                if (enableLogin) {
                    captchaCallback();
                }
            });
        }
    }
</script>

    <script type="text/javascript" src="/Scripts/jquery.tablesorter.js"></script>
    <script language="javascript">
        function UpdatePriceGuide() {
            trackEvent("Price Guide", $('#category').val(), $('#set').val());
            document.location = SITEROOT + 'price-guide/' + $('#category').val() + '/' + $('#set').val();
        }

        // add parsers for the dollar amount columns, so that dollar amounts will sort correctly
        $.tablesorter.addParser({
            // set a unique id
            id: 'dollar',
            is: function (s) {
                // return false so this parser is not auto detected
                return false;
            },
            format: function (s) {
                // format your data for normalization
                var value = s.replace(/[^0-9\.-]+/g, '');
                if (value == '')
                    return -9999.99;
                else return value;
            },
            // set type, either numeric or text
            type: 'numeric'
        });

        $(function () {

            
            $(".priceGuideTable").tablesorter({
                widthFixed: true,
                headers: {
                    3: { sorter: 'dollar' },    // Market Price
                    
                    4: { sorter: 'dollar' },    // Buylist Market Price
                    5: { sorter: 'dollar' },    // Listed Median
                    6: { sorter: false }        // Action Buttons
                },
                widgets: ['zebra']
            });
            
        });
    </script>

        .ac_even, .ac_odd, .ac_over { background: #ffffff; }
        .ac_results li:hover { background: #ffffff; }
        #sg-search-table .ac_over{
   
        background-color:#cfdde5;

<script type="text/javascript">
    $(window).on('load',function () {
        var currentLiIndex = -1;
        var listItemsInSearch;
        var listsLength;
        var rightdiv;

        $(".headerSearchBox").autocomplete("https://shop.tcgplayer.com/handler/autocomplete.ashx", {
            extraParams: {
                r: function () { return Math.floor(Math.random() * 165468787); },
                g: function () { return "Magic"; },
                ns: 'true',
                useCache: 'true'
            },
            cacheLength: 0,
            scrollHeight: 850,
            selectFirst: false,
            delay: 300,
            minChars: 1,
            matchContains: 1,
            width: 600,
            highlight: false,
            formatItem: function (data, i, n, value) {
                $('.ac_results').html(value);   // this manually places the autocomplete results in ac_results but outside the dynamically generated list elements
                currentLiIndex = -1;
                listItemsInSearch = $('.autocomplete-results').find(".autocomplete-results__result");
                listsLength = listItemsInSearch.length;
                rightdiv = $(".autocomplete-results__groups .autocomplete-results__group-result:first");

                //return value;  // commented out return (how results are normally returned to autocomplete.js) because we already manually wrote the results above
            },
            //end formatItem
            formatResult: function (data, value) {
                return $(".headerSearchBox").val();
            }
        }).click(function () {
            currentLiIndex = -1;
            $(listItemsInSearch).removeClass("ac_over");
        }).keydown(function (event) {
            if (event.which == 40) {
                currentLiIndex++;
                if (currentLiIndex >= listsLength) {
                    currentLiIndex = 0;
                }
                $(listItemsInSearch).removeClass("ac_over");
                $(listItemsInSearch).eq(currentLiIndex).addClass("ac_over");

            }
            else if (event.which == 38) {
                currentLiIndex -= 1;
                if (currentLiIndex < 0) {
                    currentLiIndex = listsLength - 1;
                }
                $(listItemsInSearch).removeClass("ac_over");
                $(listItemsInSearch).eq(currentLiIndex).addClass("ac_over");
            }
            else if (event.which == 37 || event.which == 39) {
                if (currentLiIndex !== -1) {
                    if ($(".sg-search-results-bottomright").has($(listItemsInSearch).eq(currentLiIndex)).length > 0) {
                        currentLiIndex = 0;
                    } else {
                        currentLiIndex = $(listItemsInSearch).index(rightdiv);
                    }
                    $(listItemsInSearch).removeClass("ac_over");
                    $(listItemsInSearch).eq(currentLiIndex).addClass("ac_over");
                    return false;
                }
            }
            else if (event.which == 13) {
                if (currentLiIndex == -1) {
                    window.location = 'https://shop.tcgplayer.com/productcatalog/product/show?newSearch=false&ProductType=All&IsProductNameExact=false&ProductName=' + encodeURIComponent($(".headerSearchBox").val());
                } else {
                    $(listItemsInSearch).eq(currentLiIndex).children(":first").trigger("click");
                }
            };
        });

        $(document).on("mouseenter", ".ac_results li", function () {
            currentLiIndex = $(listItemsInSearch).index($(this));
            $(listItemsInSearch).removeClass("ac_over");
            $(listItemsInSearch).eq(currentLiIndex).addClass("ac_over");
        });

        $('.dropdown-toggle').dropdown();
        $('.gameSearchDropdown').change(function () {
            $('.default').empty();
            $('<span>' + $('.gameSearchDropdown :selected').text() + '<span class="dropdown-arrow"> &#9662; </span></span>').prependTo('.default');
            $('.headerGoButton').animate({
                left: $('.default').width() + 385
            }, 300, function () {
            });
            $('.advanced-search-header').animate({
                left: $('.default').width() + 435
            }, 300, function () {
            });
            $('.gameSearchDropdown').css({ 'width': $('.default').width() + 10 });
        });

        $(document).on('click', '.dropdown-menu a', function () {
            $("a").remove(".dropdown-toggle");
            $('<a class="btn dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#"> ' + $(this).text() + ' <span class="caret"></span></a>').prependTo(".btn-group");
        });

        //start hover function for Products rollover
        $('div#products-wrapper').hover(function () {
            $('#vertical-navigation').show();
            //add vn hover
            $('#vertical-navigation').hover(function () {
                $('#vertical-navigation').show();
                $('.secondary-nav').show();
                $('.secondary-nav').css('z-index', '1000');
            }, function () {
                $('#vertical-navigation').hide();
            });
        },
            //end hover function for Products rollover
            function () {
                $('div#products-wrapper').hover(function () {
                    $('#vertical-navigation').show();
                },
                    function () {
                        $('#vertical-navigation').hide();
                    });

                $('#vertical-navigation').hide();
            });

        //end document ready
    });
</script>

            var selectedGame = document.getElementById("SearchGameName").value;
